{"tid":543049,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民重提浸大內地生野戰：當年當街做愛都未停學","createTime":"2018-01-28T06:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T14:33:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":102,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"527b93d079f11b18f0205331a12a3f278d285c02","tid":543049,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180127/large/1517058184_5de1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180127%2Flarge%2F1517058184_5de1.jpg&h=ea3d5ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浸大學生反普通話畢業標準風波持續，兩名牽頭「佔領」語文中心的學生因被指對教職員言行不當，遭勒令即時停學。浸大生前日就發起校內集會遊行，向校方表達不滿，其中有要求撤回對兩名學生的處分等。「反普考試」因facebook群組「浸大山神」而起，但由網上掀起的浸大風波豈止於此。Facebook群組「放棄治療院」前日分享了《蘋果》2年多前的新聞，當時有一對內地來港的大學生情侶在街頭「打野戰」，帖中笑言「當年咁X樣都未洗停學啦！同學！因為佢講普通話嘛」。<br />\n<br />\n當年兩名內地生街頭「打野戰」的小風波，兩名主角分別為19歲的浸大男生及一名理大女生，有指兩人將馬路當大床纏綿了45分鐘，直至警方到場大喝才醒來。由於兩人在公眾地方行為不檢，被法官判處社會服務令。「放棄治療院」發帖網民認為，當年學生在大街上激戰亦不至於處即時停學，指是因為該事主「講普通話嘛...殖民地黎架！ 講好普通話係必需架！仲有特權架」，質疑校方在兩事上做法不公、雙重標準。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，浸會大學即時停學處分所引校規已多年沒用；有指，若學生所牽涉事件一經進入法律程序，校方一般不會再作「停學處分」，以免涉事學生遭重複被罰。"},{"pid":"e4f76dfa56a0429db4120950da79f9f073b2e364","tid":543049,"uid":36104,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:22:59.000Z","msg":"因為蝗比香港人高一等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港已死，香港人淪為中國三等奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2759db748ea5bf8e702ffb43df24a535e9b348","tid":543049,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a878d5a085dba69774654d6f135438f7a13c6b","tid":543049,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:29:31.000Z","msg":"特權人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8621e4eab8711b9386740ec281e97a9631f99885","tid":543049,"uid":139139,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:49:46.000Z","msg":"因為啲高層唔會同隻狗計較囉<br />\n明知蝗蟲鍾意係街邊扑嘢<br />\n同動物冇乜分別<br />\n咁樣邊有人理佢<br />\n<br />\n但係高層就會因為小小事流放眼中釘<br />\n成日阻住晒佢哋發達<br />\n人哋要奶共，梗係要大力搞掂港獨分子啦<br />\n出師有名幾難先搵到<br />\n<br />\n咁樣都要問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67d30dd10a96f2f4a813805cddf92e280ed4063","tid":543049,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:07:47.000Z","msg":"問校長條仆街"},{"pid":"5a23854e5ba4505360a0ecba66e9c325ce62e214","tid":543049,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:08:48.000Z","msg":"因為唔係講住粗口扑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d803eb9fd2aa2dcb6f266378715e6028887cc1","tid":543049,"uid":71725,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dea30308661163c491177675effb6f2344624f78","tid":543049,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:09:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d671b6f0b3e546a22d229d48224b24e825d0f21","tid":543049,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:14:17.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 侵B<br />\nShow Blocked User - 新年毒男"},{"pid":"854bf917e87b66056030fa33168862fb4d1f063b","tid":543049,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a23854e5ba4505360a0ecba66e9c325ce62e214","tid":543049,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:08:48.000Z","msg":"因為唔係講住粗口扑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:14:50.000Z","msg":"唔知有無講&quot;操你個臭B&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3530860b91f60b74ed09806131627b23de54c5","tid":543049,"uid":47359,"lik